          "id": "tldr:2023-03-23:o009",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "TECH IPOS IN HISTORY",
          "summary": "This article goes in-depth about Shou Zi Chew's life and background. Shou Zi Chew is the CFO of Bytedance and CEO of TikTok. At 39 years old, he attended Harvard Business School and previously interned for Facebook during its start-up phase. Prior to joining Bytedance, Chew was the CFO of Xiaomi and spent two years as an investment banker at Goldman Sachs.",
